item.title: Steve Wozniak at Apps-World 2013
item.author: William F N Daubney,
item.description: Steve Wozniak, known by many as Woz was the keynote speaker of Apps-World 2013 at Earls Court, London. As a member of the press via my website, I was invited and given a press pass.
